reviewText:
Lotte is an ironclad, scissor-wielding genius with a delicate delivery and an unusually deep understanding of her craft.
She brings fantasy to life.
Fascinating, beautiful artistry combined with a lyrical interpretation of well known fairy tales.

Lotte Reiniger's work is unbelievably good!  Her storytelling is second to none, and her silhouette animation is wonderful - the cut-outs are like no others, and the movement she achieves with them - superb!
